name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-Thin', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans Thin Regular (AlegreyaSans-Thin.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Thin' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans Thin'.

Pass

Alegreya Sans Thin Italic (AlegreyaSans-ThinItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-ThinItalic', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans Thin Italic (AlegreyaSans-ThinItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Thin Italic' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans Thin' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Alegreya Sans Light Regular (AlegreyaSans-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans Light'.

Pass

Alegreya Sans Light Italic (AlegreyaSans-LightItalic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-LightItalic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Alegreya Sans Light Italic (AlegreyaSans-LightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-LightItalic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Alegreya Sans Light Italic (AlegreyaSans-LightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light Italic' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans Light' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Mac NID 6

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-Italic', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans Italic (AlegreyaSans-Italic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-Italic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Mac NID 6

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-MediumItalic', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans Medium Italic (AlegreyaSans-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium Italic' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans Medium' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Alegreya Sans Bold (AlegreyaSans-Bold.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-Bold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-BoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans ExtraBold Regular (AlegreyaSans-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-ExtraBold', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans ExtraBold Italic (AlegreyaSans-ExtraBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold Italic' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans ExtraBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Alegreya Sans Black Regular (AlegreyaSans-Black.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans Black'.

Alegreya Sans Black Italic (AlegreyaSans-BlackItalic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-BlackItalic', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans Black Italic (AlegreyaSans-BlackItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'AlegreyaSans-BlackItalic', Everything looks good.

Alegreya Sans Black Italic (AlegreyaSans-BlackItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Alegreya Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black Italic' = NID 1 'Alegreya Sans Black' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.
